{"id":16036,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":6,"day":14}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"386","ytitle":"","mtitle":"找房子","ftitle":"","authors":["汤亦可"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"汤亦可"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找住房，找住房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿马路，挨弄堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞥见红纸帖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立刻赶去望:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的写着-出卖伤风…，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的写着-天皇皇:，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的写着-下疳圣手…，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的写着-专割包皮长…，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不见“召租”字样!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔找到几张“召租”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜似接到万金家书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱起眉头仔细看；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的写着-前客堂楼五十块…，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的写着!统廂房间八十元…，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的只租有保和有眷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的人多有孩不允租，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(孕妇产后即退租)，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的预付房租几个月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的空房顶费乙千余!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)下级二层单幢房；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前客堂，后客堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二层阁，三层阁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前楼房，后楼房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶披间，亭子间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有晒台上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冬无用生火炉!暖烊烊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎夏如入蒸锅-汗洋洋!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一屋人口胜过十家村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐不安，睡不宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此下房也不易寻!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高尚住宅区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见人来往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗伏廻廊下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猫卧凉台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹦鹉时弄舌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜寻房人:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此间幽静如山林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平民住窝何处寻!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(五)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨偷偷出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚间悄悄回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕见二房东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒迁逼搬吼将来!"}]}